io.openems.edge.common.channel.doc

Class Doc

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.openems.edge.common.channel.doc.Doc

  • public class Doc
extends java.lang.Object
    Provides static meta information for a Channel using Builder pattern. Possible meta information:
    • access-mode (read-only/read-write/write-only) flag accessMode(AccessMode)
    • expected OpenemsType via getType()
    • descriptive text via getText()
    • a Unit via getUnit()
    • possible named option values as String or Enum via getOption(String), getOption(int), getOption(Enum) methods
    • importance Level via getLevel()
    • is debug mode activated via isDebug()
    • callback on initialisation of a Channel via getOnInitCallback()
